* ğŸŒ€ **Clean Dust from Fans & Vents**
  â†’ Use air blower or soft brush to clean dust from the **CPU fan**, **power supply**, and **vents**.

* â„ï¸ **Improve airflow**
  â†’ Add case fans or use a laptop cooling pad.

